@node "inst" "Getting this sod to work..."
(1) Copy all files to where they should be.

(2) Then delete them, cos you're scared.

(3) Reinstall and go through the rexx script with text editor.

(4) Change LINE=? to suit how many lines you want.

(5) Change paths to make sure they're all okay.

(6) Make sure you test this in a shell first.

(7) Untested is use of weird ansi codes ^[44;32m etc.

(8) Run from logoff script as 'c:rx bbs:utils/mcs.rexx'

Or wherever you keep rx.
Just play until you figure it.
@endnode
